undertale.desc: Undertale is an RPG game created by developer Toby Fox. It is a unique RPG experience, because unlike other RPGs, you don't need to kill monsters to finish the game. In fact, you are encouraged to use the mercy option repeatedly.

undertale_aus.desc: Undertale Alternative Universes(AUs), are variations on an original universe, in this case, Undertale.
